    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large usually circular sinks, as in industrial plants, in which a spray of water activated by a foot pedal allows several workers to wash simultaneously.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
